item.title: L i e s - Fokkses [Chill, Collab, Project, WIP]
item.dc:creator: NorthEast
item.description:
Bruh, I don’t even know anymore.

First, the person I consider the BEST Auxy remixer I’ve seen EVER needs help with a song. I mean seriously, it’s like your one influence, the person you look up to in life, asking people for help.

And second, this song is quite hard to even think up a good tune to add with it. Everyone here may have done it, but I’m pretty sure it was almost to completely impossible for them to do so, and they pushed their limits farther than normal to achieve this goal.

I’m not dissing you, but I feel like this is almost my version of your all time low, man. (Also, I’ve been watching a hell of a lot of AniSins, and now I feel like I gotta do what he does. Hang on, I think there’s a word for it…oh yeah, a phase! I’m in a phase where I gotta act like him to feel like I’m being accepted. Don’t feel like being angry with me or coming up with some rude way to insult/punish me because you didn’t like this post. But you gotta admit, someone’s otta do it, and it just so happened to be me. Seriously, though, don’t be mad. I might still need your help in the near future.)

Read full topic
